          .showcase__card(data-aos="fade-up")
            img(src='img/showcase-1.png' srcset='img/showcase-1@2x.png 2x')
            p.p-small Stay aware of the market updates and check the stock / ETF prices in real-time
        .showcase__col.swiper-slide
          .showcase__card(data-aos="fade-up")
            img(src='img/showcase-2.png' srcset='img/showcase-2@2x.png 2x')
            p.p-small Get access to 250+ stocks and ETFs on the London Stock Exchange in a tap.
        .showcase__col.swiper-slide
          .showcase__card(data-aos="fade-up")
            img(src='img/showcase-3.png' srcset='img/showcase-3@2x.png 2x')
